1. 사용자 지시
2. 본 폴더 [`CLAUDE.md`](CLAUDE.md) · [`MOVA_ERD.md`](MOVA_ERD.md)
3. [`suvisdev/_claude/CLAUDE.md`](../../../_claude/CLAUDE.md)

### Cursor 참조 예

```
@suvisdev/apps/mova/_docs/CLAUDE.md
@suvisdev/apps/mova/_docs/MOVA_ERD.md
@suvisdev/_claude/CLAUDE.md
```
